WELCOME HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS! 
THIS MCGEHEE ESTATE RARE FIND BOASTS OF  BEAUTY, SPACE, AND MORE SPACE AND IS FULLY EQUIPPED WITH CUSTOM SHUTTERS. THIS HOME HAS 4 OVERSIZED BEDROOMS 3 FULL BATHS, A SEPARATE FLEX ROOM, A DINING ROOM, A FAMILY ROOM WITH BUILT-INS, AND A FIREPLACE WITH BEAUTIFUL WOOD BEAMS ON THE CEILING. THE EAT-IN KITCHEN HAS AN EXPOSED BRICK WALL OVEN WHERE ALL APPLIANCES WILL REMAIN.  JUST A FEW MORE FEET IS A LARGE UTILITY ROOM WITH EXTRA STORAGE.  THE PRIMARY BEDROOM IS LOCATED ON THE 1ST FLOOR WITH A PRIVATE SEATING AREA. TO FURTHER YOUR ENJOYMENT WELCOME YOUR GUEST TO YOUR BEAUTIFUL BRICK COURTYARD WITH MATURE TREES AND EXTREME PRIVACY.
THE ROOF IS ABOUT 2-3 YEARS OLD, BUT A SMALL AMOUNT OF TLC WILL INCREASE YOUR INVESTMENT. THIS ONE WILL BE SOLD IN IT'S CURRENT STATE.
SINCE YOUR CURIOSITY HAS BEEN PEAKED CALL YOUR FAVORITE REALTOR AND SCHEDULE A TOUR TODAY. SEE YOU SOON!
